    "body": "I think mev-boost should respond immediately as soon as the first relay responds ok. (So it requires calling status in parallel against all relays).\n\nAnother approach could be to detach the calls. Mev-boost can do it's own polling to relays and maintain its own view of the situation, so the mev-boost can respond immediately with its current view.",
